---
// Footer.astro
---

<footer class="bg-background text-slate-600 py-16 border-t border-slate-100">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    
    <!-- Top section: Columns -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 mb-16">
      
      <!-- Brand Column (Span 4) -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-4 flex flex-col gap-6">
        <a href="https://micromanagedmedia.com/" class="flex items-center gap-3 group inline-flex mb-2">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-slate-950 border border-slate-300 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xl rounded-md transition-colors group-hover:bg-slate-800">
            M
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col -gap-1">
            <span class="font-bold text-lg leading-tight text-foreground transition-colors">MicroManaged</span>
            <span class="text-primary font-bold text-lg leading-tight">Media</span>
          </div>
        </a>
        
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Lead generation systems for local service contractors. If the phone isn't ringing, we fix that.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm border-l-2 border-slate-800 pl-4 py-1 italic">
          Founded by Bob Rutledge &mdash; 25+ years PPC experience. Serving HVAC, plumbing, roofing, electrical, and home service businesses across 50 U.S. markets.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 mt-2">
          <a href="tel:+12517650333" class="text-primary font-bold hover:text-accent hover:opacity-80 transition-colors inline-flex items-center gap-2">
